    Spotify Recently Played
  </p>
  <Image
    class="w-full dark:block hidden"
    src="https://spotify-recently-played-readme.vercel.app/api?user=4la0onkb7z65yks3gmr6yzj3o&theme=dark"
    alt="spotify dark"
    width={725}
    height={150}
  />
  <Image
    class="w-full block dark:hidden"
    src="https://spotify-recently-played-readme.vercel.app/api?user=4la0onkb7z65yks3gmr6yzj3o&theme=light"
